# CURSOR PROMPT — Bond Onboarding Platform (Phase 1 MVP)

Build a complete Next.js 14+ App Router application called "Bond Onboarding Platform." It is a multi-tenant onboarding portal for Bond Sports. Two audiences: (1) external org users who see a public checklist at `/onboard/[slug]`, and (2) internal Bond staff who manage everything from `/admin/*`. Deploy target is Vercel. Database is Supabase (Postgres + Auth + Realtime). Styling is Tailwind CSS. Use `@supabase/ssr` for auth helpers, NOT the deprecated `@supabase/auth-helpers-nextjs`.

---

